怪不得。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪不得阿斯卡綸在那時那麼痛苦，好在有他們吸引注意。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這艘船還在升高。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行駛的方向......不是戰場，這艘船在返回倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的船從倫蒂尼姆出發，朝公爵的軍艦開了一炮，在諾伯特區停了幾天。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在公爵們的戰艦快到了，你們就又要回去了？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來我要改改對曼弗雷德的印象了，他現在不光熱衷於帶孩子，還開始喜歡郊遊了？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，你什麼都不知道。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你叫什麼名字？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明椒。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來你就是明椒，我在報告裡看到過你的名字，你放了那些十一號軍工廠的工人們，被曼弗雷德逮了個正著。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這對於一個薩卡茲雇傭兵來說，是不是......不怎麼光榮？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於一個薩卡茲雇傭兵來說，光榮最可恥。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#4$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你去過卡茲戴爾，對吧？卡茲戴爾是什麼樣子的？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我以前的隊長告訴我，那裡是薩卡茲的家。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在哪裡長大？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哥倫比亞。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怪不得。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有沒去過卡茲戴爾的薩卡茲都以為那裡大概是個可愛又甜蜜的小窩。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你們的一廂情願而已。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以在你的認知中找些最骯髒、最噁心、最落魄的形容詞，然後放大一百倍，那就是卡茲戴爾。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......聽起來很難讓人喜歡。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#14$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#14$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那為什麼......那麼多的薩卡茲稱呼那裡為家？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#14$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為他們需要一個家。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們以為，只要有了一個家，一切都會好起來，那些對薩卡茲的歧視和迫害就會轉瞬消失，薩卡茲們可以再度挺起胸膛。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，愚蠢的天真。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許是因為......你不是個薩卡茲？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#13$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很喜歡提問題，小姑娘，這在戰場上可不是個好習慣。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我只是隨便猜的！請別生氣！", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#8$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我只是很好奇。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡沒什麼人會和我聊天，曼弗雷德將軍也很忙。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都很興奮，他們說自己正在投身一項偉大的事業......但是為什麼我感覺不到呢？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是看到，老面孔們一個個死掉，新的面孔很快就會頂替上來，可是等新面孔變成了老面孔......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一樣的事情就會再度發生。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我常常覺得，自己不應該在這裡。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#9$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是薩卡茲，有那麼重要嗎？", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果所有人都覺得你是個薩卡茲，那麼你最好的選擇就是磨掉角，真的假裝成一個薩卡茲。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為你只會作為一個薩卡茲生活。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在活下去面前，自己的感覺沒那麼重要。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，你參與了這一場屬於薩卡茲的戰爭？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，你該在曼弗雷德身邊待得更久些。他還沒有把那些有關戰爭最重要的知識教給你。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德將軍借了我一本《薩卡茲戰爭史》。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作者我認識，叫赫德雷，是個蠢貨。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#8$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“薩卡茲的戰爭”“維多利亞的戰爭”“公爵的戰爭”“王庭的戰爭”，說這些話的人，都是蠢貨。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#10$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰會自大到聲稱自己擁有一場戰爭？起碼我不會。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭就是戰爭，僅此而已。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不相信這場戰爭能夠拯救我們......那你相信什麼呢？", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#11$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我相信餓了要吃飯，口渴了要喝水，手臂揮久了會累，從這裡跳下去會死。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只相信這些無法被賦予意義的東西。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玩弄意義，是一切痛苦的根源。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "同樣地，我相信利益使人衝動，恐懼使人急躁，燒旺的火焰無法輕易撲滅，釀成的爭鬥無法簡單消弭。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$frontline_intro", "key": "$frontline_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲，來這裡做客，你應該先和我打個招呼。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "曼弗雷德，好久不見。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#3$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，不妨就留下來，你可以和我們一起欣賞。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風暴很快就要來了。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲與曼弗雷德一起轉頭看向窗外。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能看到遠處揚起的煙塵，數支高速戰艦編隊正在急速駛來。"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這艘高高飛起的飛空艇吸引了早就停靠在周圍的公爵部隊的全部注意。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看著這些在飛空艇的陰影中，如昆蟲一般追逐著的小小戰艦，伊內絲的心中突然閃過一絲明悟。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們要的是火苗。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，火苗已經被點燃了，你們只是......將這架飛空艇，當做把它燒旺的柴薪。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開斯特、威靈頓、溫德米爾，也許還有諾曼第......", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些貪婪公爵的代言人們如今已經齊聚在這個地塊上，他們主子的艦隊正在一邊觀察其他競爭對手的動向，一邊向這裡駛來。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這艘飛空艇的速度很慢，你們在等待他們，你們在誘惑他們。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大公爵們不會想讓飛空艇躲回牢固的倫蒂尼姆城牆之後，他們會在這裡聚集......", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你們等待的，就是這一刻。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個絕妙的......碎片大廈的靶場。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷有個敏銳的好搭檔，我該為他高興嗎？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#4$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，你發現得有些遲了。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵們，拿下她。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_419_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing1", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing1", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.4}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她和你說了什麼，明椒？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#12$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4071_peper_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說，戰爭就是戰爭，僅此而已。", "name": "明椒"}, "figure_art": "avg_4071_peper_1#3$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼......", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，僅此而已。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她可以把視野放遠些，環繞在戰爭周圍的，又有多少東西呢？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g9_airshipdockcorridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "必須把這個情報送出去。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲必須承認，軍事委員會制定了一個傑出的計劃。"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她能預想到之後會發生什麼。"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公爵們的實力會在碎片大廈引來的天災之下遭受重創，並且，這筆帳，公爵們不僅會記在薩卡茲頭上，也會記在各自的對手頭上。"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而維多利亞這種能夠引來風暴的力量，一旦被真正放在明面上，在這片大地上的任何國家都會感到恐懼，都會感到憤怒。"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每個勢力都會想毀去這種力量，或者乾脆擁有這種力量。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果此時，鎮守邊疆的公爵們，又因為彼此的爭鬥而衰落呢？"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞，烏薩斯，卡西米爾，乃至舊高盧地區，絕不會放過這個機會。"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是最初的那一團火。"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快，無法阻擋的火焰，就會迅速席捲整片大地。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲知道，現在還不算太晚，現在還有時間。"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要能把這個情報送出去——"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走廊的盡頭，陰影在靠近，那不是屬於自己的影子，那是這具軀殼的主人。"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊內絲曾在她的老搭檔那裡聽說過死魂靈的傳言，她第一次慶幸自己不是個真的薩卡茲。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是了，還有影子。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#9$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朝陽正在升起，漫長的一夜終於過去，腳下的移動地塊，被拉出了一道長長的投影。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好吧。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我該感謝自己，找了個足夠高的地方。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4087_ines_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我猜，摔這一下真的會死。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#12$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#12$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，誰能想到，有一天，總是能從死亡中歸來的伊內絲，終於要徹底擁抱它了呢。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#12$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "赫德雷和W恐怕會狠狠笑話我一頓。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#12$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望他們沒有機會看到我那副慘樣。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#12$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——呼。", "name": "伊內絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4087_ines_1#12$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glass_break"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i07", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 25.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的身體在下落，狂風吹起頭髮，幾乎睜不開眼。"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，只有在這個高度，她才能把整個諾伯特區的陰影全部納入自己的眼中。"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有在這個高度，這些她目力所及的龐大陰影才能被自己操控。"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她知道，留給自己的時間不過短短數秒，她正快速跌入眼前的陰影中。"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是現在。"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡已在門外徘徊。"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}